<p><a href="http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-11-18/u-s-agencies-to-say-bitcoins-offer-legitimate-benefits.html" onclick="javascript:_gaq.push(['_trackEvent','outbound-article','http://www.bloomberg.com']);">Bloomberg (11/18/2013) </a>-  United States agencies to say that Bitcoin offers some legitimate benefits as a currency.</p>
<p><a href="http://dealbook.nytimes.com/2013/11/18/regulators-see-value-in-bitcoin-and-investors-hasten-to-agree/?_r=0" onclick="javascript:_gaq.push(['_trackEvent','outbound-article','http://dealbook.nytimes.com']);">NY Times Dealbook (11/18/2013)</a> - Regulators and investors see value in Bitcoin.</p>
<p><a href="http://www.theverge.com/2013/11/16/5111546/new-york-state-weighs-bitlicense-certification-for-bitcoin-traders" onclick="javascript:_gaq.push(['_trackEvent','outbound-article','http://www.theverge.com']);">The Verge (11/16/2013)</a> - New York State Department of Financial Services is considering licensing Bitcoin traders.</p>
<p><a href="http://techcrunch.com/2013/11/06/the-bitcoin-bubble/" onclick="javascript:_gaq.push(['_trackEvent','outbound-article','http://techcrunch.com']);">Tech Crunch (11/06/2013)</a> - The Bitcoin bubble could burst at any time.</p>
<p><a href="http://www.coindesk.com/dumb-mistakes-costly-bitcoin-losses/" onclick="javascript:_gaq.push(['_trackEvent','outbound-article','http://www.coindesk.com']);">Coin Desk (10/24/2013) </a>- How dumb mistakes can lead to some very costly losses of digital currency.</p>
<p><a href="http://online.wsj.com/news/articles/SB10001424127887324665604579079721277783300" onclick="javascript:_gaq.push(['_trackEvent','outbound-article','http://online.wsj.com']);">Wall Street Journal (09/19/2013) </a> - Article that explains what it takes to become a Bitcoin miner.</p>
